{"tid":719453,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解毛利勝永比人低估左咁多","createTime":"2018-06-27T12:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T15:56:12.000Z","uid":47268,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f5749bb2e0067fc7f13c01bd181a9a61a3f9666f","tid":719453,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"明明同真田幸村都係大板五人眾<br />\n喺夏之陣嗰時<br />\n明明係毛利勝永打頭陣衝先<br />\n仲要突破咗敵方幾隊人<br />\n真田幸村先至衝去德川到<br />\n如果唔係毛利勝永我唔信真田可以殺入德川本陣<br />\n<br />\n之後又可以用炸藥殺退追擊既滕堂高虎<br />\n<br />\n但後世人淨係記得真田幸村"},{"pid":"ada836c0c608cf4819a0dabc1c2dc1a218dda145","tid":719453,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df9cbad9012f58c684b0cdf8e8619cbfa1c497ff","tid":719453,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"542939b84577152862f755fe1a0a44ac2348545b","tid":719453,"uid":53103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"真田幸村係冬之陣先勁,夏之陣靠毛利勝永carry全場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e34fe332bba93b6a649d3728b88ecd451712c2","tid":719453,"uid":103497,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"因為真田可以偷爆大本<br />\n毛毛得咩？開個魔免就收皮啦"},{"pid":"ce4af12d066201f8978ec081d2909e22ac08a474","tid":719453,"uid":117008,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為真田可以偷爆大本<br />\n毛毛得咩？開個魔免就收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n毛利勝永呀 講緊乜鳩都唔知 又唔撚係風趣"},{"pid":"1942629997473767b1d579fcf898530d226b5421","tid":719453,"uid":25123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"歷史係由勝利者寫嘅，戰敗者通常都好少被人寫好<br />\n而真田幸村被寫到咁勁純粹係出於政治因素，佢個年代甚至根本就冇「幸村」呢個人"},{"pid":"50b42593a98f079336a963b4015b9b118de40cb1","tid":719453,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1942629997473767b1d579fcf898530d226b5421","tid":7194